@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Khumalo Craft";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: lightgray; /* Light gray background */
            color: grey; /* Text color */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            h1

        {
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        text-align: center;
        color: tomato; /*  color for title */
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .vision-heading {
            color: blue; /* Blue color for vision heading */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: green; /* Green color for highlighted text */
        }

        .join-us {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .join-button {
            background-color: red; /* Red color for button */
            color: whitesmoke; /* White text color */
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .join-button:hover {
                background-color: darkred; /* Darker red on hover */
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium, where passion meets craftsmanship and tradition resonates in every creation. Founded by the visionary entrepreneur, James Khumalo, our mission is to bring handcrafted products from artisans worldwide to a discerning global audience.
        </p>
        <p>
            <span class="vision-heading">Our Vision:</span> At KhumaloCraft Emporium, we envision a world where the timeless beauty of handcrafted products finds appreciation across borders and cultures. We strive to create a <span class="highlight">scalable, accessible, and user-friendly platform</span> that not only showcases the richness of artisanal skills but also provides a seamless shopping experience for our customers.
        </p>
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">Challenges and Innovations:</span> Building a platform like KhumaloCraft Emporium comes with its share of challenges and opportunities. James Khumalo's vision of a globally accessible, scalable, and secure platform drives our team to innovate and overcome technical hurdles.
        </p>
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">Advanced Features:</span> In our quest to enhance user experience, KhumaloCraft Emporium offers advanced features such as search capabilities, notifications, serverless services, and automation. These functionalities are designed to streamline the shopping process and delight our customers at every step.
        </p>
        <p class="join-us">
            <span class="highlight">Join Us:</span> We invite you to explore the world of KhumaloCraft Emporium and discover the beauty of handcrafted treasures. Whether you're a connoisseur of artisanal goods or simply seeking unique pieces to adorn your home, we promise an unforgettable journey of discovery and delight.
        </p>
        <button class="join-button">Explore Now</button>
        <p>
            Thank you for choosing KhumaloCraft Emporium, where every purchase supports artisans and celebrates the timeless artistry of craftsmanship.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
